name: r-rnames
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.0.1' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-rnames
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/rnames_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/rnames/rnames_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: a7cbd8df2a12919e69cd7557ef3a1a1fd567980f3faf65fc04529fbcc2632388

build:
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/
  missing_dso_whitelist:
    - '*/R.dll'        # [win]
    - '*/Rblas.dll'    # [win]
    - '*/Rlapack.dll'  # [win]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}grep              # [win]
    - {{ posix }}findutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make              # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('rnames')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('rnames')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=rnames
  license: MIT
  summary: Recursive display of names and paths of all the items nested within sublists of a list object.
  license_family: MIT
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/MIT
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
